<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<CarouselPage xmlns="http://xamarin.com/schemas/2014/forms"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml"
             x:Class="TNO.MainPage"
             >
    <ContentPage 
        BackgroundColor="#1B2838">
        <ScrollView>
            <StackLayout>
            
                <Image x:Name="top_img1" Aspect="AspectFit"
                ></Image>
                <Image x:Name="desc" Aspect="AspectFit"
                
                   
                ></Image>
                <Label
                    Text="World War II has been over for twenty years, but its legacy still lives on. The German Reich reigns supreme from the Atlantic sea to the once great city of Moscow, ruling Europe with an iron fist. Thousands live and die everyday under German tyranny, yearning for a freedom that may never come.&#10;&#10;But all is not well in the Reich.&#10;&#10;Hitler lays on his deathbed even as the first German raumsonaut lands on the moon, and already the vultures pick at his corpse. Albert Speer, Martin Bormann, Hermann Göring and Reinhard Heydrich each prepare to take power in the Reich, and the world waits with baited breath for the storm that is surely coming. Outside of the Reichstag in the megacity of Germania, partisans prepare for their final struggle, and Heinrich Himmler plots to bring the world to the edge from his spartanist utopia in the Ordenstaat of Burgundy.&#10;&#10;Across the seas, the United States gathers allies to prevent the fall of democracy in the world, struggling to contain its own politics long enough to tear up the treaties that had ended the Second World War.&#10;&#10;In Asia, the Japanese Empire groans under the weight of rivals within as well as without, as a hundred different cultures struggle and begin to cooperate in the goal of finally overthrowing their slaveholder.&#10;&#10;In the Mediterraenan, an old alliance feuds with itself. A reformer in Italy seeks to create a hotbed of democracy in Europe as an aging Franco fights to keep control of Iberia.&#10;&#10;"
                
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
               
                ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="The world teeters in a careful balance. Will it survive to see a new millennium, or is this the beginning of the end?
"
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                
                ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="&#10;The year is 1962, and the world sits on the edge of destruction.&#10;"
                    TextColor="#4B8BB1"
                    FontSize="Medium"
                
                    ></Label>
                <Image x:Name="features" Aspect="AspectFit"></Image>
                <Label
                    Text="After years of development and two gameplay demos, The New Order: Last Days of Europe has finally been released! This mod contains the following features, among dozens of other secrets hidden throughout the game:&#10;
"
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                
                ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   Ten years or more of playable content for three German    candidates in the civil war, Japan, China, England, Italy and the   Iberian Union, Himmler's Burgundy, the United States of America and many Russian warlords."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   Five years or more of playable content for England. Yunnan, Indonesia, much of the German Unity-Pakt, German colonies in Africa, South Africa, as well as Ireland, Wales, Scotland, and some of the Italian colonies in Africa and the Middle East."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   Engage in economics that change based on your actions."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   A completely new interface for the Cold War aesthetic."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   Thousands of events written to the highest standards in Hearts of Iron writing."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   A fully reworked tech tree."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   New ideologies!"
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   An entirely new law and politics system based on Victoria 2."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   An entirely new map, built for increased detail as well as a dystopian aesthetic."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   Thousands of unique focus icons, event pictures, tech icons, and more."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   New GUIs and gameplay features for almost every playable nation, ensuring no one feels alike."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   Thousands of decisions"
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   The ability to wage nuclear war, and witness the post-apocalypse."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   Hundreds of secrets to be discovered."
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>
                <Label
                    Text="  -   And so much more!"
                    TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                    FontSize="Small"
                    ></Label>



            </StackLayout>
        </ScrollView>





    </ContentPage>
    <ContentPage
        BackgroundColor="#1B2838">
        <RelativeLayout>
            <Button
                x:Name="next"
                Clicked="next_Clicked"
                Text="->"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                FontSize="Header"
                BackgroundColor="Transparent"
                RelativeLayout.XConstraint="{ConstraintExpression Type=RelativeToParent, Property=Width, Factor=0.7}"
                RelativeLayout.YConstraint="{ConstraintExpression Property=Height, Factor=0.7}"
                RelativeLayout.WidthConstraint="150"
                RelativeLayout.HeightConstraint="150"
               
                
                ></Button>
            <Button
                x:Name="previous"
                Clicked="previous_Clicked"
                Text="&lt;-"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                FontSize="Header"
                BackgroundColor="Transparent"
                RelativeLayout.XConstraint="{ConstraintExpression Type=RelativeToParent, Property=Width, Factor=-0.07}"
                RelativeLayout.YConstraint="{ConstraintExpression Property=Height, Factor=0.7}"
                RelativeLayout.WidthConstraint="150"
                RelativeLayout.HeightConstraint="150"
               
                
                ></Button>
            <Image  x:Name="galery" Aspect="AspectFit"
                RelativeLayout.XConstraint="{ConstraintExpression Type=RelativeToParent, Property=Width, Factor=0.0}"
                RelativeLayout.YConstraint="{ConstraintExpression Property=Height, Factor=0.0}"
                RelativeLayout.WidthConstraint="500"
                RelativeLayout.HeightConstraint="500"
               
                    ></Image>
            
            

           

        </RelativeLayout>


    </ContentPage>
    <ContentPage
        BackgroundColor="#1B2838">
        <StackLayout>
            <Image x:Name="Extras"
                ></Image>
            <Label
                    Text="Bugs"
                    TextColor="#4B8BB1"
                    FontSize="Medium"
                
                    ></Label>
            <Label
                Text="While we strove to polish the release, there is no doubt there are still plenty of bugs waiting to be discovered. Please report any on our Discord here: https://discord.gg/NUmjGny, or on the Steam discussion pages."
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"
                ></Label>
            <Label
                Text="Please contain all bug reports to that link. The mod can not be downloaded from there currently, but this may become possible in the future."
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>
            <Label
                    Text="Discord"
                    TextColor="#4B8BB1"
                    FontSize="Medium"
                
                    ></Label>
            <Label
                Text="Our Discord can be found here: https://discord.gg/NUmjGny"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>
            <Label
                Text="Please read our rules and enjoy our community of over 10,000 people!"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>
            <Label
                    Text="TV Tropes"
                    TextColor="#4B8BB1"
                    FontSize="Medium"
                
                    ></Label>
            <Label
                Text="We have possibly the largest TV Tropes page for any game mod out there! Find it here: https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TheNewOrderLastDaysofEurope"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>
            <Label
                    Text="Reddit"
                    TextColor="#4B8BB1"
                    FontSize="Medium"
                
                    ></Label>
            <Label
                Text="Our Reddit can likewise be found at: https://www.reddit.com/r/TNOmod/"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>
            <Label
                    Text="Other Media"
                    TextColor="#4B8BB1"
                    FontSize="Medium"
                
                    ></Label>
            <Label
                Text="Our ModDB is rarely updated and can be found here: https://www.moddb.com/mods/a-new-order-last-days-of-europe"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>
            <Label
                Text="Our Alternatehistory.com page can be found here: https://www.alternatehistory.com/forum/threads/the-new-order-last-days-of-europe-an-axis-victory-cold-war-mod-for-hoiiv.430817/"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>
            <Label
                Text="Our ParadoxPlaza thread can be found here: https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/index.php?threads/the-new-order-last-days-of-europe.1054382/"
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>
            <Label
                Text="We are regularly posted about on SpaceBattles.com and SufficientVelocity.com, in the following threads respectively: https://forums.spacebattles.com/threads/paradox-grand-strategy-crusader-kings-europa-universalis-etc.304167/ and https://forums.sufficientvelocity.com/threads/the-hearts-of-iron-megathread.15402/."
                TextColor="#ACB2B8"
                FontSize="Small"></Label>



        </StackLayout>


    </ContentPage>

    
</CarouselPage>
